---
name: Onboard Palo Alto Networks syslog via UDP
description: |
  Reads Palo Alto Networks syslog over UDP, parses the PAN-OS CSV payload, and
  publishes parsed records to the topic `paloalto`.
---

accept_udp "udp://0.0.0.0:514"
this = data.parse_syslog()
paloalto::parse field=content
publish "paloalto"
